HEADWORD: Spearwood
<hw>Spear"wood`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>An Australian tree (<spn>Acacia Doratoxylon</spn>), and its tough
wood, used by the natives for spears.</def>⟦br⟧
